com.github.dkharrat.nexusdata.core

Class ChangedObjectsSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dkharrat.nexusdata.core.ChangedObjectsSet
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ObjectsChangedNotification

    public class ChangedObjectsSet
extends Object
    Represents a set of objects that have changed in an ObjectContext. It is used by events sent out from ObjectContextNotifier, persistence store save requests, etc.
